  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>For the price of a Coffee! Garbage Packer – A Physics-Based Garbage Truck Simulator</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Garbage Packer is a realistic Physics Based Garbage truck game! Dump dumpsters and experience realistic controls along with it!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Trucks - Side Loader, Front Loader, Rear Loader</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ability To Add Custom Skins</strong> - Join the Discord for full guide!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Map Editor -</strong> Design your own custom Maps or Get Access to other users maps in Discord!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>AI Helper -</strong> An AI helper will collect trash for you on the Rear Loader!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Physics-Based Trash Collection</strong> – Use realistic truck controls to <strong>lift dumpsters, dump trash, and crush it</strong> with the packer to maximize space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/425cd300978bd8399875e5bdd333fb27.poster.avif?t=1746942756\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/425cd300978bd8399875e5bdd333fb27.webm?t=1746942756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/425cd300978bd8399875e5bdd333fb27.mp4?t=1746942756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fully Functional Truck Cab</strong> – Features <strong>working buttons, camera system, mirrors, and an animated interior</strong> for added immersion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic Packing System</strong> – Manage your truck’s limited capacity by compacting garbage efficiently for <strong>bigger hauls and higher earnings</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/d555777a8a4ac66fdffcf74b7abeb964.poster.avif?t=1746942756\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/d555777a8a4ac66fdffcf74b7abeb964.webm?t=1746942756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/d555777a8a4ac66fdffcf74b7abeb964.mp4?t=1746942756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>First-Person and Third-Person Views</strong> – Switch between perspectives for a full <strong>driver’s experience</strong> or a better view of your surroundings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/d9451df348bda361ff7b09d7738a9f67.poster.avif?t=1746942756\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/d9451df348bda361ff7b09d7738a9f67.webm?t=1746942756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/d9451df348bda361ff7b09d7738a9f67.mp4?t=1746942756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dump out Collected Trash at the Transfer Station!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/510817d39c929f1db9ffe572efe803b9.poster.avif?t=1746942756\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/510817d39c929f1db9ffe572efe803b9.webm?t=1746942756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/510817d39c929f1db9ffe572efe803b9.mp4?t=1746942756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to <strong>build your trash empire</strong>? Get behind the wheel, start collecting, and prove your skills in <strong>Garbage Packer</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Check out the official Discord in the Discussions/Community tab!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>For the price of a Coffee! Garbage Packer – A Physics-Based Garbage Truck Simulator</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Garbage Packer is a realistic Physics Based Garbage truck game! Dump dumpsters and experience realistic controls along with it!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Trucks - Side Loader, Front Loader, Rear Loader</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ability To Add Custom Skins</strong> - Join the Discord for full guide!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Map Editor -</strong> Design your own custom Maps or Get Access to other users maps in Discord!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>AI Helper -</strong> An AI helper will collect trash for you on the Rear Loader!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Physics-Based Trash Collection</strong> – Use realistic truck controls to <strong>lift dumpsters, dump trash, and crush it</strong> with the packer to maximize space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/425cd300978bd8399875e5bdd333fb27.poster.avif?t=1746942756\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/425cd300978bd8399875e5bdd333fb27.webm?t=1746942756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/425cd300978bd8399875e5bdd333fb27.mp4?t=1746942756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fully Functional Truck Cab</strong> – Features <strong>working buttons, camera system, mirrors, and an animated interior</strong> for added immersion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic Pac